# From Jesper Norgaard Welen (2008-01-18):
# The page of the San Luis provincial government
# <a href="http://www.sanluis.gov.ar/notas.asp?idCanal=0&id=22812">
# http://www.sanluis.gov.ar/notas.asp?idCanal=0&id=22812
